This bot requires the `Guilds`, `GuildMembers`, `Messages`, `GuildBans`, `DirectMessages`, and `GuildMessages` intents to function correctly. You can enable these intents in the Discord Developer Portal under your bot's settings.

Also note that this bot requires moderation permissions (`BanMembers`) to function correctly. If it doesn't have these permissions, it will return an error when attempting to ban a user.

Lastly, always ensure that you keep your token secure and never share it publicly. If you accidentally expose your token, generate a new one immediately to prevent abuse of your bot.

